[Can't Be Grabbed and Can't Be Damaged]
author=bungholio
description=It&#039;s kind of pointless. I let the 2 fat guys pummel me but I didn&#039;t receive any damage. There were 2 dogs attacking too and I noticed they couldn&#039;t grab me like they normally do.
patch=1,EE,203D4AD8,extended,FFFFFFFF

