[Invincible]
author=bungholio
description=I only tried dogs and those big weird things with long arms. Nothing could hit me. I haven&#039;t tried the codetwink version, I don&#039;t know if this code is saveable.
patch=1,EE,21D87D0C,extended,FFFFFFFF

[Invisible and Can't be Hit]
author=bungholio
description=This would be better if this could work without making you invisible, but I don&#039;t know how to fix that because any value made you invisible. But all F&#039;s made bad things happen if you got hit or used a weapon. I couldn&#039;t remove the invisibility by making this 8-bit or 16-bit. But 103d49c0 00000000 had an interesting effect of separating Heather from her model. It&#039;s about the same except the model actually kept appearing nearby you wherever you went.
But it&#039;s bugfree as far as I can tell. Enemies will try to hit you, but their attacks go right through you.
patch=1,EE,203D49C0,extended,00000000

